snippet.title: Ardent Seas - Alpha/Development raw gameplay, Helge vs Koen
snippet.description:
Internal alpha gameplay of Ardent Seas. This is a quick match of Brawl, a game mode intended for 5-10 minute long quick games. Here I am playing with Koen, our programmer and co-lead.

I didn't upload it to the Ardent Seas channel, because of the way-too-early nature of it. As with every playtest, we found a few issues, some of which have already been fixed, too.

Website: http://www.ardentseas.com/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/Ardent_Seas
